description: Ask Kit to recommend products for your hobbies, gifts, or for getting things done.  Kit will find the best products and gear from top experts and influencers.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Kit what's the best gaming keyboard?
Alexa, ask Kit for yoga mat recommendations.
Alexa, ask Kit to recommend me hair spray.
name: Kit
shortDescription: Discover the best products and gear recommended by experts and influencers.
